Policy 4: ADMIN_TO_WAN
Purpose:
Provides the Admin VM full internet access for:
• Browsing
• Testing web filtering
• Downloading tools
• Creating malware attack simulations
Key Configuration:
• Incoming: ADMIN_LAN (port2)
• Outgoing: WAN (port1)
• Source: Admin-Subnet
• Destination: all
• Service: ALL
• NAT: ON
Resulting logs:
• Malware detection logs
• URL filtering logs
• AV file quarantine logs
• IPS alerts for risky downloads
